Phase 4: The ‚ÄúStable‚Äù Application
Here is the exact same application, but negotiated correctly.

Notice how ‚Äúcalm‚Äù the loading feels. The layout never jumps. The scroll lands exactly where you expect. It feels like a native application because we gave the browser the constraints it needed before painting.
